data.description: This lovely townhome is the Beethoven model of New Port. It's 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath and it has it all: large Owner’s Suite with walk-in closet and spa-like bath, Laundry conveniently set upstairs and a beautiful Open floor plan with your Family Room, Kitchen & Eat-In space flowing seamlessly together. Features include Kitchen stainless steel appliances, including the refrigerator, NEST digital thermostat, and so much more. HOA includes exterior maintenance, lawn maintenance, internet, cable, phone, gym, pool and more! Enjoy a shorter commute in the most affordable new homes centrally located in Hampton Roads, It's near the cascino, shopps dining, the busline and learning centers.
